Sorry for not replying to this until now.

Not sure whether you went for this on not - I notice that the deadline has =
passed.

I couldn't get the IJOPM link on pre-prints and conference publications to =
work, so I would prefer to err on the side of caution and just leave it in =
the review process for now without submitting/ publishing elsewhere.

If the IJOPM paper is unsuccessful, very happy for you to submit our paper =
for conferences as long as we don't fall foul of any pre-print publication =
and conference submission rules for other journals.

Best wishes
Caroline



