All panel/paper sessions, roundtables, lightning talks and working groups w=
ill feature a hybrid format (for in-person or virtual participation). Under=
graduate poster sessions will be held in person only.


The deadline to submit your paper, roundtable, complete panel and working g=
roup proposals to be considered for the 2026 MPSA Annual Conference program=
 is tomorrow, October 7!

The Midwest Political Science Association Annual Conference<https://go.mpsa=
net.org/e/875141/conference-/2d4myhf/1267426734/h/TqDMeyvKMmyUN1VGgu0SGtFO7=
